Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.08,0:00:05.22,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,From yesterday's me to tomorrow's me:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:09.52,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind about the lost diary pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.52,0:00:12.45,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I just tore out and threw away the pages on which I made writing mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:15.65,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have any unhappy experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:17.54,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:20.91,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It was a happiness I didn't really deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:24.59,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it was just a writing mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.19,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Something that never happened from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:29.22,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I tore them out and threw them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:33.09,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry about it, and continue living your days as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:39.93,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,And... please don't get involved with a person called Asou Renji-san from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:44.40,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It will bring unhappiness to both you and him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:48.03,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,To: tomorrow's me. From: yesterday's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:07.08,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fscy150}A
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.57,0:03:07.08,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,Note: The furigana in this episode all have the same meaning as the kanji unless specified.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:28.39,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It has already been a long thirteen hours since Chihiro and I broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:32.97,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Chihiro has already forgotten what happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:38.33,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Not just what happened yesterday, but everything since the day we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.06,0:03:41.12,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Everything about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:56.53,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro is the same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:04:00.81,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,She's the same as the Chihiro from before she met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:05.89,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why she wrote a novel like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:10.14,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll listen if you've got something to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:14.02,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It's painful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:16.87,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't be so nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:22.16,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, it will look like it's really over, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:24.16,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's really over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:29.52,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Strictly speaking, Chihiro's problem isn't that she forgets what has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:31.75,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,She can't remember it in her brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:37.06,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's a result of repeatedly losing thirteen hours of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:42.56,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Present-day medicine can't make Chihiro better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:48.00,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Even if a miracle occurs and her illness is cured, her lost memories will never come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:54.86,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, miracles don't exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:59.69,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,There are only inevitabilities and accidents, and what you're going to do. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:04.80,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's painful to be unable to reach the person you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:09.08,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,But if you keep grieving over it, the burden in your heart will just get heavier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:12.50,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, there's no way I can forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.25,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't tell you to forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:19.50,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Going on with your life while shouldering that burden is also a way to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:22.60,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell you to do that though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:28.07,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:28.93,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:34.10,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Are you always at the church because you're shouldering a burden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:36.60,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder. I've already forgotten the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:45.60,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:49.20,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:52.03,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I was just wondering what happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.32,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:58.21,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Really? By the way, isn't it almost time to submit your career interest survey?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.29,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.36,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Have you decided what you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:03.08,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:07.64,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Take your time. It's your dream after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:08.43,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:13.32,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even think about tomorrow, let alone such a distant future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.75,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be a "tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:17.88,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Renji...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:20.81,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if tomorrow never came.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.91,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't say something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:26.53,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't tomorrow possibly be a better day than today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.95,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Renji? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:39.17,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't tomorrow possibly be a better day than today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.88,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that could be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:49.18,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you grieving over, young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:50.78,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Kuze-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:53.65,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:55.18,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:07:00.18,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Human beings are cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:03.52,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's heartbreaking, I feel hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:05.23,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's painful, I feel sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:09.15,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,And, even though it's painful for me, I still eat and sleep peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:12.66,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive myself, and hence it becomes even more painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:15.62,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,But, that proves you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.01,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Kuze-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:18.11,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:20.96,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do to fulfill my dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:25.88,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see. To fulfill your dream, you need to have a dream first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:27.73,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,To have a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:31.09,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,You might think it's obvious, but it's a very important something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:35.87,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,You can have an image, a desire, or a wish of what you want to become.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:37.06,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:40.39,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I wanted to become.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:44.06,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget about it, and keep wishing for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.15,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first step to fulfilling your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:49.78,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What if the dream is something impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.50,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,You can only wait for a miracle to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:55.01,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Miracles don't exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:59.85,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,"There are only inevitabilities and accidents, and what you're going to do."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:01.37,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,That's Himura favorite phrase, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:06.03,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes the outcome of your action, which become inevitable,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:10.45,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,will overlap with accidents, and fulfill your dream unexpectedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:15.79,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if that can be called a miracle, but there's one thing I'm certain about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:19.72,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will happen if you don't wish for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.48,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.48,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Euphoric Field."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:32.21,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Wish... eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:36.24,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much I wish for them, there are things I can't do anything about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:39.75,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro's memories won't come back once they disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.51,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,The time that she spent with me has already...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:54.20,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I always felt like crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:58.97,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I always looked up at the sky because I felt like my tears were going to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.43,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:06.44,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:07.44,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:12.17,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, can I ask you something strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:16.57,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:29.04,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:35.42,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I remember everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.59,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I can't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:42.18,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,How is that... How is that possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.34,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:40.04,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to break up with Renji-kun soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:46.37,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it will be painful and lonely, I decided from the beginning that this would be the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:47.95,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I could put up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:51.25,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Because it was the last time, we kissed many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:53.97,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Because it was the last time, we did it many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:58.34,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's sad, this memory will soon disappear too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:02.06,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I think I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:07.72,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how painful it is, no matter how lonely it is, I'll forget about these feelings right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:14.68,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,But now I still remember them, so it's heartbreaking. It's very painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.68,0:11:18.59,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun's warmth still remains in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:23.11,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,To tell the truth, I want to be with Renji-kun just like this all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:24.87,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I want to feel Renji-kun all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:28.12,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I want to spend time with Renji-kun just like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.47,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to forget. I don't want to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:34.88,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to return to those empty days anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:40.13,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun was the knight who saved me from agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:46.68,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun was the prince who rescued me from inside everlasting time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:54.90,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'll forget, even though I'll disappear, I love Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:59.66,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much time passes, even if everything disappears from within me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:04.77,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,at this very moment, I love Renji-kun from the bottom my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:08.28,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun, thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:11.62,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,And... farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:29.44,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,There's still something I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:33.73,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It could be a waste of effort, but... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.38,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Even though there are still missing pages...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:49.47,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Even though there are still a lot of missing pages...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:52.42,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gather them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:54.47,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely gather all of them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:58.85,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... That's why, don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:02.36,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thirteen hours is a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:06.65,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.15,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:12.95,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I shouldn't... Even though I should forget about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:18.44,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking back on it over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:20.71,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it. I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:24.46,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I can't not think about you for thirteen hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:25.96,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.70,0:14:34.30,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:36.18,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you forget anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:39.89,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you forget no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:44.65,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:49.02,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.74,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:55.99,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:04.77,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,We'll definitely... always be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:12.37,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,I believe everyone has prayed to God at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:19.38,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they might not believe, one day they will surely make an honest prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:21.38,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Something that everyone is looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:23.54,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Something that everyone is after.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:27.08,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Something that's created from everyone's continuous wish and the bonds between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:28.86,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that's created is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:53.97,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, I told you guys to free some space on the hard drive, didn't I? I can't edit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:57.02,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,President, are you still playing with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:16:00.89,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You should give up and work on something new to change your mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:03.64,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Let me do what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.89,MainT,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:08.73,MainT,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way one of his movies would end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:14.94,MainT,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's frustrating, the movie sparkles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:18.95,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you see how it goes for a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:21.83,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You just heard today that your recovery is complete, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:26.78,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't stay still anymore. With my body feeling so light...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:28.77,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:44.67,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's for breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:50.02,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It's dinner if you consider the time. I already finished school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:52.65,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to make something complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:54.65,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to have exams soon, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:56.57,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,No problem, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:59.45,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,My brain is different from yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:04.91,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,On that subject, can't you do something about your lifestyle of sleeping during the day and waking up in the evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:07.09,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:12.26,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,We have enough time to be together, and we won't disturb each other's work and studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.67,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it all good?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:15.81,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Menu planning will be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:19.35,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Our breakfasts and dinners will be reversed, won't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:22.50,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind eating fried meat after waking up though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:25.14,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,My pride won't allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:29.53,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided that I'll come up with a breakfast menu when you get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:32.06,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You don't really need to take it too seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:34.14,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:39.82,MainT,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Because I want you to eat it while it's still warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:44.70,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, it's from Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:47.33,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, how did it go for Kei-chan this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:49.96,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Completely recovered. Going to club activities right now."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:51.58,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,So she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:54.09,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:02.45,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0003,,Don't you think Hiro-senpai is mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:05.39,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0003,,He pretended to be a perverted and geeky student,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:10.36,Main,Mizuki,0001,0001,0003,,{\fscx97}but his real identity is Shindou Nagi-sensei, whom I really admire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:13.14,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,I feel totally betrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:15.98,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,I really hate him right now. I'm extremely angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:18.52,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be that mad, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:21.36,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, are you taking Hiro-senpai's side?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:23.56,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the rumored friendship between guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:25.77,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Have you fallen for a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:27.98,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the joyful and embarrassing boys love?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:29.29,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.83,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:36.42,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,This is as far as you guys go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:37.71,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,H-Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:41.09,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Because beyond here is the place where I fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:45.47,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Well then, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.18,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Say, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:49.68,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:52.14,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:57.99,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I can now walk on my own feet. Anywhere I go, I'll be running towards it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.69,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to follow me closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:01.66,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:07.70,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I can't keep waiting forever for someone to take my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:11.20,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Kei-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:16.37,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:36.19,MainF,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:38.12,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Renji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:45.30,MainF,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You said before that you were more afraid of being forgotten than of disappearing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:49.08,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I might've said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.74,0:19:52.87,MainF,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Yeah, I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:03.84,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I liked that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:08.79,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,The quiet, empty train station where nobody came was the best place for reading alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:11.63,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,However, someone got here before me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:17.24,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That was an encounter that lasted less than forty-five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:34.18,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. It's from Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:36.00,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,What does Chihiro-chan say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:42.41,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that in order to fulfill your dream, the first step is to keep wishing for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.41,0:20:47.76,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I found my dream, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:51.62,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the color I had always been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:57.05,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't found my dream yet, but I've found my way of living.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:20:58.32,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Way of living?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:00.39,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning, to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:05.32,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I understood what kind of movies I want to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:08.90,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I want to keep running with all my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:14.20,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already satisfied that my last dream had come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:15.79,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:18.29,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,This is only the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:21.17,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I will walk down the path together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.94,0:23:13.28,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,My, good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.38,0:23:15.28,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.76,0:23:18.80,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I've made you wait for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.91,0:23:24.04,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Sorry about that, Yuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.04,0:23:27.08,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Yu-kun.
